title: Danielle Parsons, photographer
itunes:title: Danielle Parsons, photographer
description:
This week we have photographer extraordinaire Danielle Parsons on the show. I can guarantee that you have seen her photos in the past but maybe didn't make the connection. She's incredibly prolific and has an incredible eye for capturing compelling visuals. We discussed her life in Pennsylvania, imposter syndrome and how she won a contest to have her photo published on a Jones Soda bottle at age 13. This is a REALLY good episode and appreciate Danielle for her time.
